text: Renwick USD 267 is a public unified school district headquartered in Andale, Kansas, United States. The district includes the communities of Andale, Colwich, Garden Plain, north Goddard, St. Joe, St. Marks, and nearby rural areas. ==Schools== The school district currently has six schools: ; High Schools * Andale High School, 9-12 * Garden Plain High School, 9-12 ; Elmentary / Middle Schools * Andale Elementary School, K-8 * Colwich Elementary School, PreK-8 * Garden Plain Elementary School, PreK-8 * St. Marks School, K-8 ==See also== * List of high schools in Kansas * List of unified school districts in Kansas * Kansas State Department of Education * Kansas State High School Activities Association ==References== ==External links== * Category:School districts in Kansas Category:Education in Sedgwick County, Kansas
